'''瑪麗·羅德威爾'''（{{lang-en|Mary Rodwell}}，{{bd|？年|||}}）是一名[[澳洲|澳洲]][[UFO|UFO]]專家，為「澳洲[[近距離接觸|近距離接觸]]者資源網絡」（ACERN）的創始人。<ref name="韋伯">{{cite book|author1=[[阿弗雷·韋伯|阿弗雷·韋伯]]著|coauthors=許淑媛譯|title=多次元宇宙|date=2017年7月|publisher=一中心有限公司|location=台中|isbn=978-986-94891-1-9}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Truth is out there but it's being hidden, UFO expert says|url=https://www.gladstoneobserver.com.au/news/scientist-suffers-crisis-of-faith-after-experience/2267595/|accessdate=2021-01-20|date=2014-05-26|publisher=Observer|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309005847/https://www.gladstoneobserver.com.au/news/scientist-suffers-crisis-of-faith-after-experience/2267595/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=The truth is out there for WA spooks|url=https://www.perthnow.com.au/news/wa/the-truth-is-out-there-for-wa-spooks-ng-57bc37345743126b23f31d76fff4fb68|accessdate=2021-01-20|date=2013-04-21|publisher=PerthNow|language=en|archive-date=2020-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200822035015/https://www.perthnow.com.au/news/wa/the-truth-is-out-there-for-wa-spooks-ng-57bc37345743126b23f31d76fff4fb68|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Agnes Water ufologist provides a service unlike any other|url=https://www.gladstoneobserver.com.au/news/ufologist-mary-rodwell-believes-we-are-not-alone/2265400/|accessdate=2021-01-20|date=2014-05-22|publisher=Observer|language=en|archive-date=2020-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201015233149/https://www.gladstoneobserver.com.au/news/ufologist-mary-rodwell-believes-we-are-not-alone/2265400/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.news-mail.com.au/news/local-expert-are-aliens-changing-our-dna/3129388/|title=LOCAL EXPERT: Are aliens changing our DNA?|date=2017-01-06|work=NewsMail|accessdate=2021-01-20|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170107210530/https://www.news-mail.com.au/news/local-expert-are-aliens-changing-our-dna/3129388/|archivedate=2017-01-07}}</ref>

== 生平 ==
出生於[[英國|英國]]，1991年移民[[西澳洲|西澳洲]]，現居[[昆士蘭州|昆士蘭州]]<ref>{{cite web|title=About Mary Rodwell|url=https://www.alienlady.com/maryrodwel|accessdate=2021-01-20|archive-date=2021-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119222454/https://www.alienlady.com/maryrodwel|dead-url=no}}</ref>。曾當過[[護士|護士]]、[[助產士|助產士]]和[[催眠治療師|催眠治療師]]<ref name="韋伯" />{{rp|229}}。

1997年，羅德威爾創立了澳洲近距離接觸者資源網絡（ACERN），向那些自稱受到[[外星人綁架|外星人綁架]]的人士提供幫助，協助他們處理創傷。她已研究了全球超過一千六百件據稱與外星生命接觸的個案<ref name="韋伯" />{{rp|229}}，和三千多名經歷過[[超常現象|超常現象]]的人合作<ref>{{Cite web|title=UFO's make contact in South West|url=https://www.busseltonmail.com.au/story/2708495/ufos-make-contact-in-south-west/|accessdate=2021-01-20|date=2014-11-19|last=Polmear|first=Fairlea|work=Busselton-Dunsborough Mail|language=en-AU|archive-date=2014-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141122205536/http://www.busseltonmail.com.au/story/2708495/ufos-make-contact-in-south-west/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

羅德威爾也是[[艾德加·米切爾|艾德加·米切爾]]博士外星接觸研究基金會（FREE）的聯合創始人和主任<ref>{{Cite web|title=REVEALED: What happens to you after an alien encounter|url=https://www.northernstar.com.au/news/abduction-expert-sheds-new-light-on-alien-visitati/3129253/|accessdate=2021-01-20|author=|date=2017-01-06|last=Broome|first=Hamish|publisher=Northern Star|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308161011/https://www.northernstar.com.au/news/abduction-expert-sheds-new-light-on-alien-visitati/3129253/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

羅德威爾主張外星生命在遠古時期就已訪問[[地球|地球]]，他們來地球「是為了協助我們進化到另一個層級」<ref name="韋伯" />{{rp|229}}，並聲稱各國政府掩蓋了外星生命的存在<ref name=":0" />。

2010年，紀錄片《我媽跟外星人說話》（My Mum Talks To Aliens）在[[特別廣播服務公司|SBS]]電視台播出，介紹了羅德威爾的生平和研究，其兒子、自認是不明飛行物[[懷疑論|懷疑論]]者的克里斯也一同入鏡<ref name="韋伯" />{{rp|229}}<ref>{{Cite web|title=Encounter with 'Alien Lady'|url=https://www.gladstoneobserver.com.au/news/alien-obsession/707909/|accessdate=2021-01-20|date=2010-11-27|publisher=Observer|language=en|archive-date=2013-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130624093617/http://www.gladstoneobserver.com.au/news/alien-obsession/707909/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

